				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Hi!
<br />

<br />
Don't worry, everything is ok here.
<br />

<br />
It isn't a use of variable, it's an assignment to the variable. And all the following uses of the variable will use the assigned value, which is constant.
<br />

<br />
This code is used everywhere in phpBB. See, for example, the file &quot;viewtopic.php&quot;.<br />_________________<br />Oleg Parashchenko, bbAntiSpam
